          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>A <fr:em><fr:strong>displayed precategory</fr:strong></fr:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> over a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000B.xml" title="Precategory" addr="//erct/erct-000B" type="local">precategory</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>, written <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B\vdash  C]]></fr:tex>, is specified by the following data:</fr:p>
            <fr:ol><fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex>, a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {}
b]]></fr:tex> of <fr:em>displayed objects</fr:em> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex> that we shall write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b.c\in  C]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_0.c_0, b_1.c_1\in  C]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[i\colon  b_0\to  b_1]]></fr:tex>, a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001J.xml" title="Sets" addr="//erct/erct-001J" type="local">set</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C _{i}
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen b_0.c_0,b_1.c_1\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> of <fr:em>displayed arrows</fr:em> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[i]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b.c\in  C]]></fr:tex> a displayed <fr:em>identity arrow</fr:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1_{b}.1_{c}\colon  b.c\to  b.c]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[i.f\colon  b_0.c_0\to  b_1.c_1]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[j.g\colon  b_1.c_1\to  b_2.c_2]]></fr:tex>, a displayed <fr:em>composite arrow</fr:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen j\circ  i\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\circ 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen g\circ  f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\colon  b_0.c_0 \to  b_1.c_1]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>such that composition is associative and unital with respect to displayed identity arrows.</fr:li></fr:ol>
          </fr:mainmatter>
